                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "These pointed crystal shards embedded in your fingers grant you a fist Strike that deals 1d6 piercing damage, is in the brawling group, and has the magical and unarmed traits. Combat fleshgems can be enhanced with the effects of handwraps of mighty blows, as normal for an unarmed attack.",
